1. Oni su odbranili svoju zemlju od neprijateljske invazije. (*odbranili*) (They defended their country against enemy invasion.)
2. *Odbornica* je predložila novi zakon o zaštiti životinja. (Councilwoman proposed a new animal protection law.)
3. On je dao *odbranu* svog disertacionog rada pred komisijom. (He defended his dissertation in front of the committee.)
4. Pukovnik je rekao da će se *odbrana* grada izvoditi u tri faze. (The colonel said that the defense of the city would be carried out in three phases.)
5. Njihova *odbrana* bila je vrlo loša na prošloj utakmici. (Their defense was very poor in the last game.)
6. Pravna *odbrana* optuženog bila je izuzetno uspešna na suđenju. (The legal defense of the accused was extremely successful in the trial.)
7. Naša firma ima veoma dobro organizovanu *odbranu* od kibernetičkih napada. (Our company has a very well-organized defense against cyber attacks.)
8. Ovaj plan ne predviđa adekvatnu *odbranu* od prirodnih katastrofa. (This plan does not provide adequate defense against natural disasters.)